45:36.820 --> 45:38.580
♪Berlari ke bintang-bintang♪

45:38.580 --> 45:40.940
♪Tidak takut sakit♪

45:41.420 --> 45:43.460
♪Tidak pernah takut terbakar♪

45:43.460 --> 45:48.020
